---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Perro Dinero
cover_path: img/perro_dinero.png
---

<section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-16 justify-evenly space-y-4">
  <div class="rounded-full self-center">
    {% image "img/david_y_nina.png" | url, "Yo, David, y Nina, mi perra, felices en un parque.", "(min-width: 200px)
    400px" %}
  </div>
  <h1 class="font-black text-center sm:text-left text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl break-normal">
    El dinero <br><span class="text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-dark-500"> sí compra</span> <br>la felicidad
  </h1>
</section>

<hr>

<p class="text-4xl">Posts 📝</p>

{% set maxPosts = 3 %}
{% set postsList = collections.posts | head(-maxPosts) %}
{% set postsListCount = collections.postsAndBooks | length %}
<section class="flex flex-col my-4">
  {% for post in postsList | reverse %}
    {% include "postitem.njk" %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<a class="button--outline block mt-4" href="/posts/">Todos los posts 📂 ({{ postsListCount }})</a>

<hr>

<p class="text-4xl">Ensayos atómicos ✍️</p>

{% set microEssaysList = collections.micro_essays | head(-3) %}
{% set microEssaysCount = collections.micro_essays | length %}
<section class="flex flex-col my-4">
  {% for essay in microEssaysList | reverse %}
    {% include "micro_essay_item.njk" %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<a class="button--outline block mt-4" href="/ensayosatomicos/">Todos los ensayos 📂 ({{ microEssaysCount }})</a>

<hr>

<section class="mt-8 mb-8 p-4 rounded-lg bg-accent-100 dark:bg-foreground-dark text-center">
  <h2 class="mb-4 text-center font-black">Actualizaciones <span class="text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-dark-500">perronas</span> 🐕 💌</h2>

  <ul>
    <li class="mb-4">Nudismo financiero 😳</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Historias personales, de éxito y fracaso 📈📉</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Opiniones de libros, apps y hechos modernos 📚📰</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Recursos para enriquecer la mente y la cartera 🧠💰</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Directo en tu correo 📬</li>
    <li class="font-black">Una vez por semana— Cero spam 🚫</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="animate-bounce text-4xl mt-4">👇🏼</div>

  <div data-id="substack-embed"></div>

  <p>Puedes revisar los <a href="https://perrodinero.substack.com/archive">correos anteriores aquí</a>, para que veas que están perrones.</p>
</section>
